content: azep-ninja: Merged 6 PRs this month, focusing on adding "suppress action ability" to multiple platforms (Twitter #3286, Telegram #3285, Discord #3284) and making significant optimizations to the quick-intel plugin (#3208, +4034/-141 lines) and RAG context (#3248, +1692/-1259 lines). Contributed substantial code changes across 120 files with a total of +2815/-2963 lines, showing a pattern of impactful but sporadic activity on just 3 days this month. The work was evenly split between feature development and bug fixes, with particular emphasis on platform-specific action suppression capabilities and performance improvements.
